{
  "stem": "214.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the Americans, maybe say, maybe a week, maybe weeks later, started filling up those barracks with the displaced persons and-- and started sending them home, repatriating them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those French went home first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Belgians went home second.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we were left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were the Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we-- and-- and at that time, they still did not know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Poles, our good friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we decided-- you know, we felt-- I mean, we really felt, in a way, you know, sort of freer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so we decided we have to go to this American and tell him who we are and that we really do not want to remain here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That we want to go to Stuttgart to find out if there are any other Jews left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this fellow, we hit upon a Texan, who had no idea, I think, about the Holocaust, who was sitting and strumming.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll never forget-- the guitar singing [INAUDIBLE], which we'd never heard, but now I know this by-- music by heart.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] Melody by heart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we finally tried to explain to him why we wanted to go to Stuttgart, so he says, well, you know, there is no transportation left for anybody.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it's only the-- war [INAUDIBLE] ended.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as soon as I can help you with something-- and at that time, he became sort of our friend.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every morning, he called me in and gave us a small piece of Hershey bars to divide in five to five.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we thought it was something terrific.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so at that moment, we decided we are going to tell our friends who we are.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They asked us why did we go in?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
